                        <interp inst="t18370703-name-573" type="surname" value="KINGSFORD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370703-name-573" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KINGSFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I superintend the business of Thomas Kingsford, a baker at Deptford—he is in partnership with Charles Kingsford. On the 26th of June I saw the prisoner leave the bakehouse, and I suspected he had flour on his person—I had two officers in view—I beckoned to them,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183707030080"></xptr>
               <p>they came and searched him, and found this flour on him, and the bread in his hat—we have been robbed to a considerable extent.</p>
